# Content & Tests Guide

## Test vs Lesson — Key Differences

Tests have **3 files only** (no `content.ts`, no `workbook.ts`):

```
src/content/tests/test-lessons-X-Y/
  ├── metadata.ts     — id, number, afterLesson, title, totalPoints, introText
  ├── exercises.ts    — ALL exercises grouped by section (listening, reading, grammar, writing)
  └── index.ts        — assembles TestData with sections array
```

After creating the files, register the test in [src/content/index.ts](mdc:src/content/index.ts):
- Add entry to `testFolderMap`
- Verify the `navItems` array has the correct `label` for the sidebar

